      "body" : "oh, @luke-jr can you elaborate?\r\nEdit:\r\nCan't we mix that intentional design and the one that check the balance by something like :\r\n* No [minconf] provided : no balance check\r\n* [minconf] provided : actually using it (and therefore check the balance accordingly)\r\n\r\nI see no reason why one would provide [minconf] and intentionally don't want to actually check the balance.",
