      "body" : "I agree.\r\nThing is it's currently not consistent -- and worse, [minconf] despite being an argument supposed to prevent some damage, is not used.\r\n\r\nHowever I don't see why one would use send* (that is : externally) without checking the balance. What happen to other accounts if one account become negative? A positive account will not be able to spend his funds because another is indebted? Family drama!",
