      "body" : "@paraboul: confirmation tracking through 'moves' is non-trivial.\r\n\r\nE.g. lets say I send 11 BTC to an address associated with account A, and it gets 1 confirmation.\r\n\r\nThen I:\r\n  move accountA accountB 3\r\n  move accountB accountC 1 6  <-- does this succeed or fail ?\r\n",
