      "body" : "... should fail until the original coins get 6 confirmations.  There is no code to track which inputs are 'moved' by a 'move'. And, actually, the code would have to track partial inputs. And what happens if you setaccount the address that originally received the coins away from accountA ?\r\n\r\nChanging this would require a ton of work and a long QA test plan to get it all correct. I don't think it is worth it.\r\n",
