      "body" : "@luke-jr My original idea was just to use \"account\" as a ledger.\r\nThat is : using the balance of each account in order to implement a simple exchange system.\r\nMy idea was : if two users are on the same wallet : do the transaction off-the-network (move) instead of a regular sendfrom(). For this I needed to check that the sender has enough funds confirmed by 6 blocks (hence the move [minconf]).\r\nBut I guess that writing my own ledger/account system is a better idea.\r\n",
